import org.apache.spark.sql.types.FloatType
val mapping = spark.read.csv("s3://fullcontact-enrichment/pitneybowes/20210210sovrn/").toDF("fcid","street_address","city","state","zip_code","country","precision_code","pb_key","first_name","last_name","address_public","name_public","address_belief","name_belief")

val pb_mapping = mapping.withColumn("address_belief", 'address_belief.cast(FloatType)).withColumn("name_belief", 'name_belief.cast(FloatType)).withColumnRenamed("fcid", "pb_fcid").filter('address_belief > 0.89 && 'name_belief > 0.89).select('pb_fcid, 'pb_key as "pbkey", 'name_belief).groupBy('pb_fcid).agg(collect_set(struct("name_belief","pbkey")) as "key_belief").select('pb_fcid, sort_array('key_belief, false).getItem(0).as("one_key_belief")("pbkey") as "pbkey").distinct

val combined_df_pbkey = socials_full_grouped.join(pb_mapping, socials_full_grouped("fcid")===pb_mapping("pb_fcid"),"left").drop("pb_fcid")
